desc: Wedding décor consignment store located in Ebensburg PA

layout.text:
Welcome! 
206 E High Street Ebensburg Pa 15931.
Store Hours: Tue, Thurs and Sat 12pm to 4pm, Wed and Fri 4 to 8pm
Closed Sundays and Mondays
SHIP AT YOUR OWN RISK or In Store Pickup Available
Click the Catalog button above or scroll to the bottom of the page and click on a collection to browse our selection of gently used wedding décor and gowns.   We are a consignment resale store with a variety options for your wedding.   Please join our Facebook group page so see newly posted merchandise and any weather related changes to hours
Please Note: Because we are a consignment store, all sales are final. We cannot refund, replace or exchange
